        "description": "使用不同Si/Al比（5和11）和Ni含量（5%至20%）的Ni/HY催化剂，在390°C和3MPa条件下将棕榈油转化为航空生物燃料，研究催化剂组成对烷烃和芳烃选择性的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "Conversion of palm oil into jet biofuel using Ni/HY catalysts of different Si/Al ratios and Ni contents... when the Si/Al ratio of the zeolite HY was increased from 5 to 11... the ratio of alkane in the fuel decreased from 80 to 71%, and the arene ratio increased from 20 to 29%.",
